  "title": "Security Officer",
  "description": "<p>· Ensure consultants/visitors and workers do facial recognition attendance record before entering the worksite site</p>\n<p>· Report daily manpower to site management personnel</p>\n<p>· Do random check on validity of workers work permit while entering the worksite</p>\n<p>· Ensure workers entering the worksite wears safety helmet and safety shoes before allowing him to enter the worksite</p>\n<p>· Liaise with traffic controller for vehicle movement at site main entrance</p>\n<p>· Daily record visitor record book / vehicle numbers entering and exiting the worksite</p>\n<p>· Occasionally patrol the site and report any suspicious person, events or objects to safety officer</p>\n<p>· Report to safety officer if any other security related issues</p>\n<p>· Any other security and health related duties assigned by site management personnel</p>",
